                    Join our community and expierence the ultimate power-up.</p>
                    <a href="workouts"><p>START</p></a>
            </div>
            <img src="./assets/images/gamer_man.jpg" alt="gamer gym man">
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="./assets/images/girl-gym.jpg" alt="gamer gym girl">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>Level up your fitness</h1>
                <p>Discover the power of fitness and gaming, improve your focus, enhance your reflexes, and join a
                    strong community of like-minded gamers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="card">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>Start Your Fitness Journey Today</h1>
                <p>Join our community and start your fitness journey. Get access to exclusive workouts, nutrition plans,
                    and a community of like-minded gamers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-image">
                <img src="./assets/images/ryu_review.png" alt="gamer gym">
            </div>
            <div class="review-text">
                <p id="stars"> &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;</p>
                <p><em>Hadouken! Gamer Fit has transformed my training with dynamic workouts, customizable routines, and
                        a supportive community. This app melds the discipline of martial arts with the excitement of
                        gaming, pushing me to new heights. If you want to unleash your inner warrior and rise to the
                        top, Gamer Fit is your ultimate training partner.</em></p>
                <p>-Ryu</p>
